{"name":"Arcane Circle","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/pentacle.svg","system":{"class":"Arcanist","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>After you willingly <strong>dismiss </strong>an Arcanum on your turn during a conflict, if that Arcanum had not been <strong>summoned </strong>during this same turn and you have an <strong>arcane </strong>weapon equipped, you may immediately perform the Spell action for free. The spell you cast this way must have a <strong>total Mind Point cost of [SL x 5] or lower</strong> (you must still pay the spell's MP cost).</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":0,"max":4},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.8DMGkQ3b1P2usROp"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.4.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679066867254,"modifiedTime":1679067445165,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"0wOOBFKZSw0TVKfL"}
{"name":"High Speed","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/speedometer.svg","system":{"class":"Rogue","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>At the start of a conflict, you may spend 10 Mind Points. If you do, choose one option and apply it before the start of the first round:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a weapon you have equipped.</li>\n<li>Perform a <strong>Hinder </strong>or <strong>Objective </strong>action.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You also gain a bonus equal to <strong>[SL] </strong>to all Checks you perform as part of the chosen option.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":3},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.aL73dH6lAWphhIIU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685069138455,"modifiedTime":1685071043806,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"18XfLWXv7I9n6QNH"}
