{"name":"Beyond the Realms of Death","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/raise-zombie.svg","system":{"class":"Necromancer","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>When another creature you can see loses Hit Points while in <strong>Crisis</strong>, if they are not <strong>undead</strong>, you gain <strong>1 Grave Point</strong>. You may never have more than <strong>[SL + 1]</strong> Grave points.</p>\n<p>When you are reduced to 0 Hit Points, you <strong>lose all Grave Points</strong>; then, if you lost at least 1 Grave Points this way and this is the <strong>first time</strong> you are reduced to 0 HP during this scene, you do not <strong>Surrender</strong> nor <strong>Sacrifice </strong>yourself: instead, you recover an amount of HP equal to <strong>[SL, multiplied by the amount of Grave Points lost this way]</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":0,"max":5},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[{"label":"Beyond the Realms of Death","icon":"icons/svg/aura.svg","origin":"Item.ELdLekmhdP7I7gAH","disabled":true,"_id":"FBTbrIXEIr730zkQ","changes":[{"key":"system.gp.enabled","mode":5,"value":"true","priority":null}],"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"combat":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{}}],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ELdLekmhdP7I7gAH"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1684700488066,"modifiedTime":1684701061543,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"4JiyWae0C2FehNFz"}
