{"name":"Faithful Companion","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/sitting-dog.svg","system":{"class":"Wayfarer","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>Together with the rest of your group, design a <strong>level 5 beast, construct, element,</strong> or <strong>plant </strong>creature that becomes your <strong>companion</strong>. This creature has <strong>no Initiative score</strong> and <strong>does not level up</strong>, can have <strong>up to two basic attacks</strong>, gains a bonus equal to <strong>[SL]</strong> to Accuracy Checks and Magic Checks, and their maximum Hit Points are equal to <strong>[(SL multiplied by the companion's base Might die size) + half your level]</strong>.</p>\n<p>Your companion doesn't get a turn during conflicts, but on you rturn you can use an action to have the companion perform an action (only once per turn). If you leave a scene, your companion leaves with you.</p>\n<p>If your companion falls to 0 Hit Points, they flee and rejoin you at the start of the next scene in which you are present, with HP equal to their <strong>Crisis </strong>score.</p>\n<p>When you <strong>rest</strong>, your companion also gains the full benefits of resting.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":5},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4OVXOku5R1gxxcVk"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685123401665,"modifiedTime":1685139435600,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"DLOs3KneGzBWPIUE"}
{"name":"Adversity","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/internal-injury.svg","system":{"class":"Darkblade","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>As long as you are suffering from one or more status effects, you gain a +1 bonus on all Checks for every status effect you are suffering from, and you deal 2 extra damage for every status effect you are suffering from (be it with attacks, spells, Arcana, items, or any other method).</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered the <strong>Darkblade </strong>Class.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.lKVvsTomYU6jSxJs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685140644799,"modifiedTime":1685152775179,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"ERI1bXSmPQnDTv42"}
{"name":"Protect","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/surrounded-shield.svg","system":{"class":"Guardian","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When another creature is threatened by an <strong>attack, spell,</strong> or other <strong>danger</strong>, you may take their place (any Checks that are part of the danger will be performed against you; you may declare the use of this Skill <strong>before or after</strong> the Checks have been made). If the danger already affected you, it affects you <strong>twice </strong>(resolve both instances separately); you also cannot protect multiple creatures from the same danger. If you use this Skill during a conflict, you cannot use it again until the start of your next turn.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xo8cZCHkojZNG9Gr"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685063540877,"modifiedTime":1685064113157,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Frkg8fMGpfw8Qg6Y"}
