{"name":"Spell Mimic","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/carnival-mask.svg","system":{"class":"Chimerist","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>When you see a creature belonging to the <strong>beast</strong>, <strong>monster</strong>, or <strong>plant </strong>Species cast a spell, you may immediately choose to learn that spell as a Chimerist spell of your own: if you do, record the <strong>Species </strong>of the creature you learned it from.</p>\n<p>When you first acquire this Skill, choose<strong> [INS + WLP] or [MIG + WLP]</strong>. From now on, your offensive Chimerist spells will use the chosen Attributes for the Magic Check, regardless of the Attributes used by the creature you learned the spell from.</p>\n<p>You may have <strong>up to [SL + 2] different Chimerist spells</strong> memorized this way. If you want to memorize a new Chimerist spell but are already at your limit, you must forget one of your old spells and replace it with the new spell.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":0,"max":10},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.WjFph6yuzCji4uOh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.4.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679121074219,"modifiedTime":1679121518486,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"IhuZzQLw3yMMHFVR"}
{"name":"Encourage","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/thumb-up.svg","system":{"class":"Orator","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>During a conflict, you may use an action and spend 5 Mind Points to choose another creature that can hear and understand you. That creature recovers <strong>[SL x 5]</strong> Hit Points and chooses <strong>Dexterity, Insight, Might,</strong> or <strong>Willpower</strong>: they treat the chose Attribute as being one die size higher (up to a maximum of <strong>d12</strong>) until the start of your next turn.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":4},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.HEvSAHVlBe00P7sh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685066694685,"modifiedTime":1685067859778,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"JBurKK0ak1E0Qua3"}
{"name":"Breach","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/cracked-shield.svg","system":{"class":"Weaponmaster","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>You may use an action and spend 5 Mind Points to perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a <strong>melee </strong>weapon you have equipped. This attack must target <strong>a single creature</strong>. If the attack is successful, it deals no damage and you choose one option:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>You destroy one shield equipped by the target.</li>\n<li>You destroy the target's equipped armor</li>\n<li>Whenever the target suffers damage from a source before the start of your next turn, that source deals <strong>[SL x 2]</strong> extra damage to them.</li>\n</ol>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":3},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.GKIVh4Hmn9uJKwMT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685139777913,"modifiedTime":1685140563601,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"JIphqFPtUwvVb8XT"}
{"name":"Monkey Grip","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/monkey.svg","system":{"class":"Fury","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>You may equip two-handed weapons belonging to the <strong>flail, heavy, spear,</strong> or <strong>sword </strong>Categories in a single hand slot.</p>\n<p>This allows you, for instance, to enjoy the benefits of<em><strong> two-weapon fighting</strong></em> while wielding a pair of two-handed weapons, <strong>or</strong> to equip a two-handed weapon in your <strong>main hand slot</strong> and a shield in your <strong>off-hand slot</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered the <strong>Fury </strong>Class.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.qRJzVa2E8WDyB1bT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685151892756,"modifiedTime":1685152787472,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"L5al8eG7ph5R8x9e"}
