{"name":"Harvester of Sorrow","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/reaper-scythe.svg","system":{"class":"Necromancer or Entropist","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you cast the <em><strong>Drain Spirit</strong></em> or <em><strong>Drain Vigor</strong></em> spells, the amount of Mind Points or Hit Points you recover is <strong>equal </strong>to the MP or HP loss suffered by the target, respectively (instead of being halved).</p>\n<p>Additionally, your <em><strong>Drain Spirit</strong></em> causes the target to lose <strong>[HR + 20]</strong> Mind Points if you are level <strong>20 or higher</strong>, or<strong> [HR + 25]</strong> Mind points if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>, instead of the normal <strong>[HR + 15]</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Entropist </strong>and <strong>Necromancer</strong>, and must have learned <strong>both </strong>the <em><strong>Drain Spirit</strong></em> and <em><strong>Drain Vigor</strong></em> spells.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.VXI1w9qoDLA9Scdf"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1684985375219,"modifiedTime":1684985695268,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Linew26qw2Xyuang"}
