{"name":"Dual Shieldbearer","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/shield-opposition.svg","system":{"class":"Guardian","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>You may now equip a <strong>shield </strong>in your <strong>main hand</strong> slot. As long as you have two shields equipped, you gain the benefits of both items and may treat them as the following combined two-handed melee <strong>brawling </strong>weapon:</p>\n<p><strong>Twin Shields</strong>: Accuracy<strong> [MIG + MIG]</strong> | Damage <strong>[HR + 5] physical</strong></p>\n<p>Deals extra damage equal to your <strong>[SL]</strong> in <em><strong>defensive mastery</strong></em>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xafzp5SKIIsMvsdz"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685062693723,"modifiedTime":1685064111053,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"M3a4xFRxjKeeDoPO"}
{"name":"Hawkeye","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/eye-target.svg","system":{"class":"Sharpshooter","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you perform the <strong>Guard </strong>action, if you choose <strong>not </strong>to provide cover to another creature, you may choose one option:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The next <strong>ranged</strong> attack you perform before the end of the current scene will deal <strong>[SL x 2]</strong> extra damage.</li>\n<li>You may immediately perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a <strong>bow </strong>or <strong>firearm </strong>you have equipped, treating your <strong>High Roll (HR)</strong> as 0 when calculating damage dealt by this attack.</li>\n</ol>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":5},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4dd5BoHnP0Sg2egs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685071582180,"modifiedTime":1685072049449,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MWPmYgcFd0uIJR2b"}
{"name":"Shadow Strike","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/shadow-grasp.svg","system":{"class":"Darkblade","schemaVersion":"1.01","notes":"<p>You have learned to channel your vital force into your attacks. You may use an action to perform a <strong>Shadow Strike</strong>: roll your current <strong>Might </strong>die and lose an amount of Hit Points equal to <strong>[the number rolled on your Might die]</strong>. If this didn't reduce your Hit Points to 0, you may perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a weapon you have equipped: if this attack hits one or more targets, it deals extra damage equal to<strong> [SL + the number rolled on your Might die]</strong>. However, all damage dealt by this attack becomes <strong>dark </strong>and its damage type cannot be changed.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":5},"isHeroic":false},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mcyd63iARPFzgdLw"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1684979498508,"modifiedTime":1684979854910,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"N46ezcK9M7Xiww1d"}
{"name":"Heartbreaker","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/broken-heart.svg","system":{"class":"Darkblade","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you hit a creature with an attack, if that attack <strong>only </strong>targeted that creature and you have a <strong>Bond </strong>towards them, you may choose to spend half of your current Hit Points, rounded down. If you do, the attack deals extra damage equal to <strong>[10 multiplied by the strength of your Bond towards the target]</strong>.</p>\n<p>You may use this Skill only on your turn during a conflict, and <strong>only once per turn</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered the <strong>Darkblade </strong>Class.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jQnHPkiLzRpiXAcW"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685141687472,"modifiedTime":1685152784552,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"NA9EOiF8cRToMpHg"}
