{"name":"Barrage","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/striking-arrows.svg","system":{"class":"Sharpshooter","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you perform a <strong>ranged </strong>attack, you may spend 10 Mind Points to choose one option:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The attack gains <strong>multi (2)</strong>.</li>\n<li>Increase the attack's <strong>multi </strong>property by one, up to a maximum of <strong>multi (3)</strong>.</li>\n</ol>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tRwDHYwDFIbEsLTa"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685071179714,"modifiedTime":1685071994625,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"OXRePVXl6fisnZbu"}
