{"name":"Disarming Rhetoric","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/drop-weapon.svg","system":{"class":"Orator","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>During a conflict scene, you may use an action and choose a <strong>soldier</strong>-rank creature that can hear and understand you. If that creature is <strong>shaken </strong>or in <strong>Crisis</strong>, you may spend an amount of Mind Points equal to <strong>[20 + half that creature's level]</strong> to have them peacefully leave the conflict.</p>\n<p>Describe how you convince them to desist.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered the <strong>Orator </strong>Class.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vQCNCEoLBE4p2AIX"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685141187246,"modifiedTime":1685153012020,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"SYHB8sG8HXiQ8axf"}
