{"name":"Flash of Insight","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/light-bulb.svg","system":{"class":"Loremaster","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you roll a <strong>13 or higher</strong> on a Check performed to investigate a creature, item, or location -- this includes using the <strong>Study </strong>action during a conflict -- you may ask the Game Master up to <strong>[SL]</strong> questions concerning the subject of your investigation. You may ask these questions immediately or save them for later; whenever you ask one of these questions, the Game Master will answer truthfully and you will describe your character's deductive process.</p>\n<p>This Skill may only be used once on the same creature, item or location.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":3},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZEIeZoI147dl8HJT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.8","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685064542254,"modifiedTime":1685066181431,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"ZDEF87HMbnhl2if8"}
