{"name":"Revelation","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/hydra.svg","system":{"class":"Arcanist","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>You make contact with an unknown Arcanum and bind it to your soul. This Arcanum must be something you design together with the rest of the group: as long as you live, no one else in your world will be able to bind that Arcanum.</p>\n<p>Once per scene while you are <strong>merged </strong>with an Arcanum, you may use an action and spend 2 Fabula Points to <strong>trigger </strong>that Arcanum's <strong>dismiss </strong>effect (if any) without dismissing them. Doing so <strong>does not</strong> trigger the <em><strong>Arcane Circle</strong></em> Skill.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered the <strong>Arcanist </strong>Class.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.2BJNE2ZVF2kw9phi"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685155520333,"modifiedTime":1685156532818,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"LJiNnFuY5YnZgIfO"}
