{"name":"Double or Nothing","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/double-fish.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>Before you perform an Accuracy Check, a Magic Check for an offensive spell, or a Check to advance or turn back a Clock, you may declare <strong>double or nothing</strong>. If you do and the Check triggers a <strong>critical success, double</strong> the damage dealt by that attack or spell or the filled or erased sections of that Clock respectively; however, any other Result is considered a <strong>critical failure</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KZpnnO4OnSVBdFUT"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685157227725,"modifiedTime":1685158741146,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"SW8DTU3pIm50mX3x"}
