{"name":"Magic Cards","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/stack.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>You gain a <strong>deck</strong>, a <strong>hand </strong>and a<strong> discard pile</strong>.</p>\n<p>During a conflict, you may use an action and spend up to <strong>[10 + (SL x 5)]</strong> Mind Points (minimum 10). If you do, <strong>resolve 1 card</strong> from your <strong>hand </strong>for every 5 MP spent this way (to a maximum of 5 cards; these cards form a <strong>set</strong>). After you resolve the effect of the <strong>set </strong>(if any), <strong>discard </strong>these cards and draw that many cards from your <strong>deck</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":3},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Na4GpgmuAAjiLwN5"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685157494488,"modifiedTime":1685158745356,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"TP4uZGJ8yhhfqX5b"}
{"name":"Mulligan","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/card-discard.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>At the end of your turn during a conflict, you may discard up to <strong>[SL]</strong> cards from your <strong>hand</strong>. If you do, draw that many cards from your <strong>deck</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":5},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wR7pwVr68K8zEouM"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685157727659,"modifiedTime":1685158746737,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"MZHt1wXyd8S4Tf1C"}
{"name":"Trap Card","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/mantrap.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>After an enemy you can see performs an action during a conflict, you may declare one of your <strong>deck</strong>'s <strong>suits </strong>(after the action has been resolved) and put the first card on the bottom of your <strong>deck </strong>in your<strong> discard pile</strong>, face up. If that <strong>card </strong>is a joker or its <strong>suit </strong>matches the one you declared, you may immediately perform the <strong>Spell </strong>action for free, casting a spell with a <strong>total Mind Point cost equal to or lower than [SL x 5]</strong> (you must still pay its MP cost).</p>","hasLevels":true,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":4},"isHeroic":false,"requirements":""},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KM6Z14ItT6r9KY39"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685157815394,"modifiedTime":1685158748306,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"pc7VlZXtKHMHTLrW"}
{"name":"Black & White","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/yin-yang.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards, Darkblade, Entropist, and Spiritist","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you resolve the <em><strong>Double Trouble</strong></em> effect, you may have all of its damage become <strong>light </strong>or <strong>dark </strong>(instead of being a type matching the <strong>suits </strong>of the resolved cards).</p>\n<p>Additionally, as long as there is a <strong>joker </strong>in your <strong>discard pile</strong>, all damage dealt by your <em><strong>Blinding Flush, Double Trouble,</strong></em> and <em><strong>Magic Flush</strong></em> effects ignores Immunities and Resistances.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Ace of Cards, Darkblade, Entropist,</strong> and <strong>Spiritist</strong>, and you must have acquired the <em><strong>Magic Cards</strong></em> Skill.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7mqCp6MhQVV2fIMe"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685158851493,"modifiedTime":1685160528380,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"vamq7JIj06M0GR6g"}
{"name":"Forbidden Rite","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/pentagram-rose.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards or Arcanist","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>As long as there are <strong>one or more</strong> <strong>cards </strong>in your <strong>discard pile</strong>, you have Resistance to the damage type matching the <strong>suit </strong>of the card <strong>on top</strong> of your <strong>discard pile</strong> (if that card is a <strong>joker</strong>, you have Resistance to all four damage types: <strong>air, earth, fire,</strong> and <strong>ice</strong>).</p>\n<p>You also get an additional effect added to your sets. Consult the book for more information.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Ace of Cards</strong> and <strong>Arcanist</strong>, and you must have acquired <strong>3 Skill Levels</strong> in the <em><strong>Magic Cards</strong></em> Skill.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hF7D096nj0op8ChK"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685160163971,"modifiedTime":1685160570055,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"v2tB4ANZMS7DBnt1"}
{"name":"Duel Master","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/duel.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards, Fury, Rogue, Sharpshooter, and Weaponmaster","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>When you resolve the <em><strong>Magic Pair</strong></em> effect, if you attack with a weapon belonging to the <strong>arcane </strong>or <strong>thrown </strong>Category, you deal extra damage equal to <strong>[the common value of the resolved cards]</strong> and regain an amount of Mind Points equal to <strong>[twice the common value of the resolved cards]</strong> (for instance, resolving a pair of 5s will allow you to deal 5 extra damage and regain 10 Mind Points).</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Ace of Cards, Fury, Rogue, Sharpshooter,</strong> and <strong>Weaponmaster</strong>, and you must have acquired the <em><strong>Magic Cards </strong></em>Skill.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.87h6l0ACFVs6bmii"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685159764178,"modifiedTime":1685160628147,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"UrPPYJkzbi3Z309b"}
{"name":"Card Vanguard","type":"skill","img":"systems/fabulaultima/assets/icons/chess-knight.svg","system":{"class":"Ace of Cards","schemaVersion":"1.03","notes":"<p>During a conflict, if you have <strong>two or fewer vanguard cards</strong> in play, you can use an action to choose <strong>1 card</strong> from your <strong>hand </strong>and place it face down as a <strong>vanguard card</strong>; if you do, draw 1 card from your <strong>deck</strong>.</p>\n<p>When you suffer damage, if you have one or more<strong> vanguard cards</strong> in play, you may reveal one of them and place it on top of your <strong>discard pile</strong>: if you do and that card is a <strong>joker </strong>or its <strong>suit </strong>matches the type of damage you suffered, you instead suffer no damage and regain an equal amount of Mind Points.</p>\n<p>At the end of each conflict, if you have one or more <strong>vanguard cards </strong>in play, shuffle them back into your <strong>deck</strong>.</p>","hasLevels":false,"skillLevel":{"value":1,"max":1},"isHeroic":true,"requirements":"<p>You must have mastered the <strong>Ace of Cards</strong> Class, and must have acquired the <em><strong>Magic Cards</strong></em> Skill.</p>"},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.XiGjgaq6KCtlgzdb"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"fabulaultima","systemVersion":"0.6.10","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685159126742,"modifiedTime":1685160789335,"lastModifiedBy":"jqXkiXaQTTrIXvYj"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"lLgkfrX1AlwkedSa"}
